      <title>尼日利亚监管机构称丹格特寻求柴油进口禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/nigerian-regulator-says-dangote-seeking-import-ban-on-diesel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚监管机构负责人表示，阿里科·丹格特已要求尼日利亚暂停进口柴油和航空燃料，此举将使他的炼油厂获得这些产品的销售垄断权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/nigerian-regulator-says-dangote-seeking-import-ban-on-diesel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 13:19:55 GMT</pubDate>
